    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This unit remains mechanically robust with the critical VANOS system serviced and a reinforced rear subframe to maintain structural rigidity under high lateral loads. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry is dialed in, retaining the original balance of the chassis. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and a valve clearance adjustment. While showing honest patina consistent with its mileage, the powertrain remains a testament to BMW M engineering. A true enthusiast's example ready for the B-roads.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
